attributes.title: My mom got run away and eaten because of this app 🤪
attributes.review: I downloaded this app because I wanted to know more about our stinky president and see if he was really worth voting for (news flash he’s not). After the app successfully downloaded and I opened it, a semi truck crashed into my living room and completely ran over my mom. I was horrified, devastated, and I completely blame the president and this app for this tragic accident. I’m sure this app brings bad vibes and with its voodoo magic, it made the truck swerve off the road and into my house. I’d like to also add that twenty starving tigers wandered into the house and ate my mom’s bloody body. -100/10 would not recommend this app if you love you mom, if you don’t, definitely get this app. 😘

attributes.title: This App got me sick
attributes.review: When I downloaded this app, I was hoping I would gain more truthful information about our wonderful president. But I was betrayed! When I opened the app I heard a strange noise coming from my closet. My dog wouldn’t stop staring and growling at it, so I opened it (as a white person should do in situations like these). I was horrified as a massive cheese ball lunged at me! It was speaking incomplete sentences and threw cow poop in my face—I blacked out a few moments later. I don’t know what happened to the cheese ball. I have been sick for a few days now. PLEASE do not download this horrid app😊🧚🏻‍♀️✨💖🌈
